<p>
  <span class="nym">Gentle</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>gentilis</i> 'Gentile, non-Jew; heathen, pagan; of the same clan, tribe, or family' developing into <span class="lang">Old French</span> <i>gentil</i> 'high-born, noble'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


